genresAdvancedInfo.name: voetbal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Voetbal is a music genre hailing from the Netherlands that takes inspiration from traditional Dutch folk music. It is recognizable by its lively and optimistic sound, which frequently incorporates instruments like accordion, banjo, and mandolin. The lyrics typically revolve around football (soccer), celebrating the sport and its delights. Voetbal enjoys significant popularity in the Netherlands and is often played at football matches.
